{"tid":839194,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"＊有冇巴絲唔要iTunes卡可以讓比我","createTime":"2018-09-27T17:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T16:39:19.000Z","uid":58038,"like":4,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"003b3a1571c6f05a51a557c508ced9dd5e814781","tid":839194,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買iTunes卡<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買iTunes卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想去Roselia event 買張iTunes卡幾千蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾千蚊食到一日了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge iTunes卡讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位清明快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋願望除左Event當選 武士道執柒之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有幾張iTunes卡 等自己做到電競選手為港爭光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/015112_ae7ca6cc7bf52d6068cf7afa50aee12e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F015112_ae7ca6cc7bf52d6068cf7afa50aee12e.jpg&h=68899b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然隻game未出<br />\n但見到d聲優表已經知道係神game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小藍有個夢想係可以做到電競選手為港爭光... 希望咁多位動物台手畜可以幫個忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時做到世界冠軍實唔會唔記得感激一眾手畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申自問幾有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬事俱備 只欠東風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c1f0705d0f440db4e4b339123c267dae67a72d","tid":839194,"uid":86378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a0fe5d031801026c8c4f159c8e61fa901eb9f3","tid":839194,"uid":28983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"On撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523b5946e7eaa0d4c3305613fc771d7d4103f2ee","tid":839194,"uid":138355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"小學畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65006b9d54727acbb366c083e4ae19ffa11e5b1a","tid":839194,"uid":191815,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"兩舊水都無 仲有錢上連登嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5346d0b42eb29f3de77b0300749619b4dadfe5","tid":839194,"uid":206119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"789a90ffee6729cdd1cb93988512574b61b82352","tid":839194,"uid":25769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc08cbcf76fe596091aad84da5df79f1dcc26355","tid":839194,"uid":63167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:13:10.000Z","msg":"假膠"},{"pid":"8fdfc434cf635da481a26e96c316ea106b5a38f4","tid":839194,"uid":121697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"18770732666915dbe305fc4d43849e6fa9017307","tid":839194,"uid":79266,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲銀行有錢可以